+summaryLines.push(`- The stage_iv-by-liver_mets interaction was ${fmt(interactions.stage_liver.interaction.beta)} months (p=${pFmt(interactions.stage_liver.interaction.p)}), and the brain_mets-by-pleural_effusion interaction was ${fmt(interactions.brain_pleural.interaction.beta)} months (p=${pFmt(interactions.brain_pleural.interaction.p)}). These did not show large synergistic worsening beyond additive main effects.`);
